CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 14, 1958, pg. 1, reads: "Prove Asset to Homicide Bureau - Negro Detectives Trap Blair Murderer - Solve Blair Murder - Homicide Detectives Charles Brevard and Laverne Mills compare notes shortly after they had completed a 12-day investigation of the murder of Grocer Alfred T. Blair, and arrested William Thomas Hayes. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Homicide detectives Charles Brevard and Laverne Mills standing on sidewalk
